# Live tab — optional for local dev.
#
# **Easiest:** leave `VITE_FPL_PROXY_URL` commented out. `npm run dev` then uses Vite’s
# `/__fpl/*` proxy (fantasy + draft APIs) — no Cloudflare deploy needed.
#
# **Or** set your Worker URL (same as GitHub Actions secret). The Worker must include the
# `draft/*` → draft.premierleague.com route (see web/workers/fpl-proxy). If you see 404 on
# draft picks, redeploy that worker: `cd web/workers/fpl-proxy && npx wrangler deploy`
#
#   cp .env.local.example .env.local
#   npm run dev

# VITE_FPL_PROXY_URL=https://tclot-fpl-proxy.YOUR_SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev
